title: Feed The Earthlings
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Pizza, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, British
description: An all-vegan pizza and takeaway place. Also available are burgers, burritos, hot dogs and more. Part of Pizzarea Capalaba, but a completely vegan branch located in the Gold Coast. As of Feb 2016, cash only; please inquire. Menu is posted on the Facebook page. You can also buy their frozen pizzas from Plant-Based Foods. Directions: The 739 and 742 buses stop right outside. Jump off at Currumburra Rd, near Corporation Rd (South), or Koonan Crt (North) Ashmore.
